Qualifications
Requirements:
3-5 years of experience in a similar role (with F2P games);
Passion for video games and game development;
Proficiency with gameplay design, events and player experience design;
Knowledge of game design theory and deep understanding of gameplay fundamentals;
Knowledge of the F2P gaming market and current trends;
Profound gaming experience on mobile and other platforms;
English (full working proficiency);
Proficiency with game editors and prototyping tools;
Strong pitching and presentation skills
Would be considered a plus:
Programming, scripting, 2D or 3D art, scriptwriting or video directing working background;
Special education in game design, architecture, psychology or computer programming.
